Package service

Class InitialisationService

java.lang.Object
service.InitialisationService
public class InitialisationService extends Object
Service responsible for initializing the system with data from Excel files. This class handles the creation and persistence of initial data for:
  • Patients
  • Staff (Doctors, Nurses, Pharmacists, Administrators)
  • Medicines
The service reads data from Excel files and creates corresponding objects with default passwords and necessary validation.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Russell Arvin

  • Method Details

    • initialise

      public String initialise()
      Initializes the system by creating all necessary entities if they don't exist. This method checks if administrators exist before initializing to prevent duplicate initialization.
      Returns:
      null if initialization is successful, error message if an exception occurs
